{"type":"question","id":22129,"title":"多国禁出口粮食 中国会爆发粮食危机吗？","uid":9304,"topics":[2019,161],"contents":"为了应对新冠病毒疫情可能带来的影响，一些国家的政府考虑到本国的粮食安全而启动储备计划，禁止部分农产品的出口。作为粮食进口大国的中国会受到什么影响？隔离等防疫措施是否会阻碍春耕生产？<br>\n<br>\n为了确保本国粮食储备不受新冠病毒疫情打击，数个主要粮食出口国近期纷纷宣布禁止出口部分农产品，其中包括俄罗斯暂停出口去壳谷物；哈萨克斯坦则是禁止小麦粉、糖、葵花籽油的出口；越南也停止出口大米。这种储备粮食的浪潮引发外界对国际供应链可能会遭到干扰的担心。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUCyrgJVAAEZND6?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUCyrgJVAAEZND6?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUCyrgJVAAEZND6?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUCyrqIUUAEbR7y?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUCyrqIUUAEbR7y?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUCyrqIUUAEbR7y?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUCyrgJUcAAqtmC?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUCyrgJUcAAqtmC?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUCyrgJUcAAqtmC?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\nhttps://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/huanjing/hj-03262020121244.html?utm_source=dlvr.it&amp;utm_medium=twitter","date":"2020-03-27","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":3}